C               **    %LOOP                                         **
C               **    XCOOR YCOOR LINETO                            **
C               **    %END LOOP                                     **
C               **    STROKE                                        **
C               **  REFERENCE--POSTSCRIPT LANGUAGE TUTORIAL AND     **
