C     UPDATED         --JANUARY  1989.  SUN (BY BILL ANDERSON)
C                                      DRIVER OBSOLETE
C     UPDATED         --JANUARY  1989.  POSTSCRIPT (BY ALAN HECKERT)
C     UPDATED         --JANUARY  1989.  CGM (BY ALAN HECKERT)
