C               **  ALONG WITH INTEGER COORDINATES,                 **
C               **  AND THE LB (= LABEL) INSTRUCTION                **
C               **  AND THE DESIRED TEXT STRING,                    **
C               **  AND ETX TO DENOTE THE END OF TEXT STRING,       **
