 9110 CONTINUE
      GOTO9000
C
C               ******************************************************
C               **  STEP 96--                                       **
C               **  TREAT THE X11        CASE                       **
C               **  NOTE THAT JUSTIFICATION, POSITIONING, ETC. IS   **
C               **  HANDLED BY THE C ROUTINE.  ALSO, THE CHARACTER  **
C               **  STRING IS PASSED TO C AS AN INTEGER ARRAY       **
